    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Once per turn, when you would deal damage to a creature with a melee weapon or Taijutsu attack, you can choose to make an additional attack as a part of the same action at a -5 penalty to the attack roll. <br />If you would score a successful hit, you can repeat this attack one additional time. <br />Until the beginning of your next turn, creatures gain advantage on attacks targeting you after using this trait.</p>",
